    <MissileTemplate>
      <AssociatedTemplateName>SGM-H-320 Atlatl</AssociatedTemplateName>
      <Designation>SGM-H-320</Designation>
      <Nickname>Atlatl</Nickname>
      <Description>$MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_CRUISE - $MISSILESEEKER_MODE_ACTIVE_ABBREV(&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;RADAR&lt;/color&gt;)/[$MISSILESEEKER_MODE_PASSIVE_ABBREV(&lt;color=#7CC6BC&gt;EO&lt;/color&gt;)] - $MISSILEWARHEAD_SHORT_HEKP</Description>
      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-H-320 Atlatl&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 3 waypoint-capable cruise missile.  It is based on the SGM-H-3 body, which is a high speed hybrid missile designed to strike heavy targets.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_HEKP warhead.  It homes in on its target using an Active Radar seeker, validating that it is the correct target using a Passive Electro-Optical seeker.

$MISSILESTAT_CONTROLMETHOD: $MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_CRUISE_LONG
$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE: &lt;b&gt;&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_POS&lt;/color&gt;	&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_TRACK[+$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_TRP]&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt;

$MISSILESTAT_PRIMARYSEEKER: $MISSILESEEKER_MODE_ACTIVE_CAPS &lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;RADAR&lt;/color&gt;
$MISSILESTAT_VALIDATOR: $MISSILESEEKER_MODE_PASSIVE_CAPS (&lt;color=#7CC6BC&gt;EO&lt;/color&gt;)

&lt;b&gt;Cruise&lt;/b&gt;
